<TEXT>
   Actor Willem Dafoe, who plays Jesus in
``The Last Temptation of Christ,'' is a Christian who would not do
anything blasphemous, his parents say.
   ``We are proud of our son and we trust his judgment,'' Muriel
Dafoe said Friday. ``He was brought up in a Christian home, and he
